;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;　　1、经商是公事：经商不是“私事”，是为了众人，为了社会而进行的“公事”。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;#39;Helvetica Neue&amp;#39;, Helvetica, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;　　2、得到客户喜爱：要努力做到让客户认为是你在卖，所以愿意买。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;#39;Helvetica Neue&amp;#39;, Helvetica, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;　　3、把商品当做自己的女儿：抱着把客户当做自己女儿婆婆的想法，就能够超越简单的买卖，结成更深一步的信任关系。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;#39;Helvetica Neue&amp;#39;, Helvetica, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;　　4、经商是真刀真枪一决胜负：真刀真枪决斗，胜负必居其一，经商也用这种思想去努力，一定能顺利进行。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;#39;Helvetica Neue&amp;#39;, Helvetica, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;　　5、堂堂正正地盈利：利益是对为社会提供服务的报酬，应该堂堂正正地获取合理的利益。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;#39;Helvetica Neue&amp;#39;, Helvetica, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;　　6、为客户合掌：当客户离开，面对他的背影，发自内心地合掌感谢。这样的店铺，人们自然会聚集过去。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;#39;Helvetica Neue&amp;#39;, Helvetica, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB";s:4:"date";s:10:"2016-06-20";}}